close_reason: Completed planned scope for Remove session-based ownership model and preserved verification context for future changes.
body: "Context: session ownership came from Pi todos heritage and is no longer appropriate for multi-agent usage. Approach: migrate assigned_to_session to assignee and remove PM_SESSION and settings.session.id references while preserving deterministic behavior and lock safety."
